text: Had curry fish head & prawn ball here! Food was great! Atmosphere was good! My partner enjoyed having his beer there!
Charged $75 for small steamed fish for one person. Not worth it at all. Better ask price before you order. This place is ripoff if donâ€™t ask how much. Disappointed

They will charge you extra for credit card and not tell you. Asked for a napkin and they said I had to pay extra. The waitress was extremely rude. My fried rice was ok. Lots of oil and carrots in the omelette. Never again!
